---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — EMI Calculator"
  description="Learn about EMI Calculator, a free online tool that helps you calculate loan EMIs, total interest, and amortization schedules instantly."
>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-6" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
      About EMI Calculator
    </h1>

    <div class="surface-card p-6 sm:p-8">
      <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">
        <p>
          EMI Calculator is a free online tool built for one purpose: to help you calculate your monthly loan payment in under 30 seconds. Whether you're considering a home loan, car loan, or personal loan, our calculator gives you a clear picture of what you'll owe each month — and how much of that goes toward interest.
        </p>
        <p>
          We built this tool because most EMI calculators online are cluttered with ads, slow to load, and missing key features. Ours is fast, works on any device, and lets you compare both reducing balance and flat rate methods — something most calculators don't offer. You can also switch between Indian Rupees (₹) and US Dollars ($) with a single tap.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our calculator uses the same standard formulas that banks like SBI, HDFC, ICICI, and major US lenders use. The full amortization schedule shows you exactly how your loan balance decreases over time, month by month. No sign-up, no hidden fees, no data collection — just a straightforward tool that helps you make better borrowing decisions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
